item.description:
One of my fave groups is playing at Princeton Station, check them out at www.RockCityBand.com.

I probably won't be doing dinner there, as single checks are such a problemo...so if anyone gets there early for dinner, and can print out some "meetup" signs, it would be great. I'll def be there by 8-8:30 for introductions, before the band starts. If you get there AFTER the music starts, I'll probably be on the dance floor, so you're on your own for intros...lol.

no cover charge and you can dress "down" if you like ;)

Hope to boogie with you soon, suz
item.how_to_find_us: hopefully you can see "meetup" signs on the tables, if not look for the rowdy group

group.name: Fun in So. NH and Merrimack Valley
